data.description: Welcome to a great family home that anyone would be proud to call home!  This great large floorplan offers large rooms and a nice huge covered-patio that extends your home outside rain or shine.  The two full bathrooms have been upgraded and enhanced. The primary retreat starts with a large private bedroom, which flows into the "SPA-like", beautifully done primary bath. The large walk-in closet completes the primary suite. A great kitchen layout opens to a large family area and breakfast room.  The formal dining room is spacious and can fit a big dining table with several chairs.  Upstairs features an oversized open Game-room with 3 large bedrooms and an updated bathroom.  This home has a full house GENERAC Generator which like everything has been well maintained.   Installed in 2018, the AC has been well maintained as have the Low E windows also installed in 2018. A new roof was put on in 2015. A 12' X 14" like-new storage unit is in great shape and will be left for the new owners.
